# Vendor Shop Management System

## Features
- Vendor Authentication (Register/Login)
- JWT Token Based Security
- Shop CRUD Operations
- Nearby Shop Search API

## Setup
1. Clone the repository
2. Create a virtual environment
3. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
4. Run the application: `uvicorn main:app --reload`

## API Endpoints
- POST /register: Register a new vendor
- POST /token: Login and get JWT token
- POST /shops: Create a new shop (Authenticated)
- GET /shops: List vendor's shops (Authenticated)
- PUT /shops/{shop_id}: Update a shop (Authenticated)
- DELETE /shops/{shop_id}: Delete a shop (Authenticated)
- GET /search: Search nearby shops (Public)

## Authentication
Use the /token endpoint to get a JWT token. Include the token in the Authorization header for authenticated routes.
